{"tid":2192624,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（年經）玄鐵劍法勁啲定獨孤九劍勁啲","createTime":"2020-09-07T08:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T02:55:31.000Z","uid":217162,"like":17,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"68cea8d926542f373c0fba3e5b12b9bd6b101e3f","tid":2192624,"uid":217162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:44:02.000Z","msg":"個人認為玄鐵劍勁啲 因為玄鐵劍純粹就係劈同斬<br />\n其實呢個根本唔可以叫做招式 只係一個普通用劍嘅方法 仲要講明大巧不工 即係唔需要啲咩技巧 <br />\n<br />\n相反九劍係防反 本身都需要對劍法要有一定嘅認識 同埋小說講過求敗曾經用紫微軟劍誤傷人 而大師兄初初學識嘅時候 都試過傷到師父 而且個人認為九劍要用軟劍先可以發揮最大嘅效果 基於呢個假設 即係表示紫微軟劍所用嘅劍法就係九劍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n玄鐵劍法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n獨孤九劍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97df06eb4aa15723d973da53ef887ccb02823d1c","tid":2192624,"uid":231583,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:45:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d9aff646b9107ee2f5273dda818eb5502f6c3cb","tid":2192624,"uid":217162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97df06eb4aa15723d973da53ef887ccb02823d1c","tid":2192624,"uid":231583,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:45:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:48:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4fe0b7558f033e64a31b41640c0d9839da70929","tid":2192624,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:52:00.000Z","msg":"破氣式就係玄鐵劍法"},{"pid":"6eae496e125ffb6dcc339e66ed60ed91a8e5efde","tid":2192624,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:54:00.000Z","msg":"我褲浪把巨劍最勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d237a5eb4a0995f302a9e2e7b8bbd303686f66e1","tid":2192624,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,